title: WATERFRONT, Lake Roesiger
posting_body: LAKE ROESIGER, SNOHOMISH, WATERFRONT, 2 BEDROOM, 1BATH, furnished, new windows, up to date appliances, 1100 sq ft house, available SEPTEMBER To May 15th, large deck, dock/boathouse, year round fishing,
RENT $2,000.00/mo, plus first, last and security deposit.
Screening fee per person living in the home 18 years of age and older.
NO PETS, NO SMOKING, provide professional and personal references.
Rent per month includes septic and water.
Only serious applicants and those who follow COVID-19 screening guidelines and vaccinated.
Tour by appointment available for qualified applicants, contact info
General Qualifications and Information for Applicants
- No negative rental or mortgage history
- No balances due to prior Landlords/Agents
